  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The city council will meet in\nspecial session at o'clock tonight,\npursuant to call from Mayor\nDaggett, for the purpose Of taking\naction on the proposals of the\nTraction company and the Wash\nington Water Power company Of\nfering to stand half the expense Of\nnew bridges recommended by the\nboard of public works.\n\n\nOther matters may be brought\nbefore the council."
    }
